<title>SOUTH AFRICA: BOLTONS FOOTWEAR YR SHR, DIV DOWN.</title>
<headline>BOLTONS FOOTWEAR YR SHR, DIV DOWN.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended February 28, 1997</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)	 </p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)     24.3	  vs 28.2</p>
<p>    Div (cts)	    5.5 making 8.0 vs  8.5 </p>
